      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example of a modern classic, striking a balance between daily utility and pride of ownership. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though as expected with regular use, there are minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch. All glass is clear and free of cracks. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats show light bolster wear but no punctures or thinning, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the cold AC and the premium sound system. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced strictly at 5,000-mile intervals, with a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection completed just last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and is free of any unusual noises or warning lights. This is an honest, dependable vehicle that has been cared for by a non-smoker and is ready for the road.",
